    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shyondemic 是一款毛毛城市中的疫情生存游戏！<br>这是一座被疫情袭击的兽人都市，灵感来源于现实中的新冠病毒（COVID-19）。游戏将隔离与求生的压力，转化成一场轻松又带点疯狂的冒险。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你将扮演拉米娜（Lamina）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303740/extras/90444ffcdd591e61f5139765cf104b95.avif?t=1767764642\" width=800 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一只害羞的哈士奇女孩，刚搬到大都市「努桑卡」。<br>但就在她搬来后的第一天，疫情就爆发了——她不得不把自己隔离在公寓里。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>别太菜，不然就会被奇怪的液体“液化”</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这就是你菜出事后的拉米娜：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303740/extras/ffa4ae0717967020cf5422f280f2ad50.avif?t=1767764642\" width=128 height=128 /></span>（图片闪烁警告！如对闪烁画面敏感请注意）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情丰富，拥有 6 种不同结局！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >洗澡（水是救命道具）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >西米液（别碰这玩意！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电脑（宅到不沾阳光的快乐生活）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303740/extras/305aafd935bebd19e1fc39ec8f76fa6d.webp?t=1767764642\" width=16 height=16 /></span>瓶子翻转挑战（Bottle Flip）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的朋友们（就像你一样！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的画风与原创歌曲</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >烹饪（让她自由发挥！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几乎由一个人独立完成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 - 6 小时可完成一个结局</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>其他特性：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拉米娜可以使用她的电脑进行各种操作：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >线上购物<br>自由职业平台</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >社交媒体<br>加密货币交易、挖矿<br>赌博游戏（别沉迷）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天物价都会飞涨，所以你必须好好管理你的经济！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>道具系统丰富：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水枪<br>水手雷<br>水陷阱<br>水瓶<br>除臭剂<br>Floff香皂<br>升级书<br>可升级的属性装备</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>还有更多疯狂内容：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梗图（Memes）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boykisser（你懂的）</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这些男孩们正在偷偷看着你...</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >等着你把游戏加入愿望单：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303740/extras/d2a5bb9738eed1c54a5bedd699179faa.avif?t=1767764642\" width=128 height=128 /></span> Boy1 正在盯着你……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303740/extras/d2a5bb9738eed1c54a5bedd699179faa.avif?t=1767764642\" width=128 height=128 /></span> Boy2 也在看着你……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303740/extras/d2a5bb9738eed1c54a5bedd699179faa.avif?t=1767764642\" width=128 height=128 /></span> Boy3 还是在看着你……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快把我们加入愿望单吧！</h2>",
